														<p></p>
														<h3>Can you vape this product by itself?</h3>
														<p style="padding-left: 30px;">We do not recommend vaping this product on its own. The vape juice additive is for people who love to vape other products but would like to add or maximize the CBD benefits to their current vape liquids. You can add this product to any e-liquid or vape oil of your choice.</p>
														<h3>Why is the bottle not full?</h3>
														<p style="padding-left: 30px;">We utilize a 5ml bottle for both the 1,000mg and 2,000mg vape juice. Both bottles are filled at approximately 3.75ml level. To keep a high concentration of CBD in this additive, we do not use any additional filler solutions which would defeat the purpose of having a low volume/high strength product to add to existing vape products without impacting their characteristics.</p>
