														<h3>What are Isolated Spectrum Tincture Products?</h3>
														<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Our Isolated Spectrum Products are manufactured with purified isolated CBD. The isolate tincture features non-detectable levels of THC, meaning that THC compounds are not found with our instrumentation during our testing process.</p>
														<h3>Is there a difference in the formula for the human and the pet tincture?</h3>
